nodes.text: This female attendant lived in the Outbound Flight Colony in 22 ABY. That year, she was assigned to watch after the colony's Force-sensitive children while they were quarantined due to fears that they could be trained as Jedi. She worked alongside an older woman. She briefly met Commander Chak Fel, who found the prison while exploring the colony, and initially mistook him for Perry, a Peacekeeper assigned to the Quarantine zone.
